title: Contact with duplicated number
content:
Pixel 2 XL
No root
Android 10
Contacts app version 3.23.1.31

I have a contact that on Contacts web is displayed with one number only in format +39 xxxxx, but on the phone is displayed with two duplicated numbers one in format +39 xxxxx and one simply as xxxxxx, yet if I go into edit I see only one number in format +39 xxxxx
